data.description: Welcome home to this classic 2-bed, 2-bath ranch with potential for a third bedroom in the walkout basement. Rich hardwood and new vinyl plank flooring throughout complement the new appliances in the spacious kitchen, complete with a large pantry. Gather in the family room in the basement around the wet bar. Enjoy the convenience of a large attached garage and a large 24x40 pole barn with optional heating. Stay cozy with both propane and wood heat options. Relax on the back decks overlooking the large fenced in back yard and the picturesque marsh on this serene 3.24 acre property. Ideal for outdoor enthusiasts, this property also features a smoker, a wood shed with loads of seasoned firewood, a fire pit, and an additional 10 by 12 building with loft. Make this your dream home. Move now!
